quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  4,113,"Si wanaano ЖЃural Alla ngal e dow maaЙ—a e Yurmeende Makko nden, fedde goo e maЙ“Й“e himmirayno majjinngol ma, Й“e alaa e majjinnde si wanaa pittaali maЙ“Й“e Й—in, Й“e lorrirtaama hay e huunde. Alla Jippinii e maaЙ—a Deftere nden e Г‘eeГ±al ngal, O Anndinii ma huunde nden a anndaano. ЖЃural Alla ngal e dow maaЙ—a laatike mawnungal"
  4,114,"MoЖґЖґere alaa e ko heewi e yeewtere maЙ“Й“e nden, si wanaa on yamirЙ—o sadaka, maa moЖґЖґere maa moЖґЖґiЕ‹tingol hakkunde yimЙ“e Й“en. Kala waЙ—irЙ—o Й—um Й—aЙ“Й“ugol welayee Alla, arma Men Okka mo njoЙ“di mawndi"
  4,115,"Kala on lunndiiЙ—o NulaaЙ—o on Й“aawo nde paawal ngal Й“anngani mo, o jokki ko wanaa laawol gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, Men HucciЕ‹tinay mo e kon ko o hucciti, Men Naadoya mo Jahannanma, nge bonii ruttorde"